召唤一个全身皮甲、拿石头和原石的僵尸是
setblock ~ ~2 ~ mob_spawner 0 replace {MaxSpawnDelay:10,MinSpawnDelay:10,SpawnCount:1,Delay:10,RequiredPlayerRange:200,SpawnRange:10,MaxNearbyEntities:5,SpawnData:{id:Zombie,HandItems:[{id:"minecraft:stone"},{id:"minecraft:cobblestone"}],ArmorItems:[{id:"minecraft:leather_boots"},{id:"minecraft:leather_leggings"},{id:"minecraft:leather_chestplate"},{id:"minecraft:leather_helmet"}]}}


你可以注意到，刷怪笼生成什么生物由Spawndata里的id决定，Spawndata内部还可以加相应实体的各种NBT。而且SpawnPotentials内部也有少许变化，生成的实体id到了Entity内部
